         \u00a0\n      </div>\n<div id=\"content_wrapper\">\n<div id=\"ad_wrapper\">\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n\tjQuery(function() {\n   \t    var pull        = $('#pull');\n            menu        = $('#header .navigation ul');\n            menuImage = $('#header img.menu');\n            mobileMenu        = $('#pull-menu-mobile');\n            search = $('img.search-icon');\n            searchBar = $('div.search');\n            searchClick = false;\n            search.on('click', function() {\n                  searchBar.slideToggle();\n                  searchClick = true;\n            });  \n     \t    $(menuImage).on('click', function(e) {\n\t        //e.preventDefault();\n                if (!searchClick) {\n                  menu.slideToggle();\n                }\n                searchClick = false;\n\t    });\n           /* pullMobile.on('click', function(e) {\n              e.preventDefault();\n                if (!searchClick) {\n                  mobileMenu.slideToggle();\n                }\n                searchClick = false;\n\t    });*/\n            \n\t});\n\tkpath = '/'; kda_top(); kda_sid_init(); kda_sid_n=3;\n\t</script>\n</div> <div class=\"breadcumb\">\n<br/>\n<a href=\"/\">KDnuggets Home</a> \u00bb <a href=\"/news/index.html\">News</a> \u00bb <a href=\"/2016/index.html\">2016</a> \u00bb <a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/2016/04/index.html\">Apr</a> \u00bb <a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/2016/04/news-features.html\">News, Features</a> \u00bb IDC/KDnuggets Advanced Analytics Survey \u2013 please participate (\u00a0<a href=\"/2016/n13.html\">16:n13</a>\u00a0)    </div>\n<div class=\"single\" id=\"content\">\n<div id=\"post-header\">\n<h1 id=\"title\">IDC/KDnuggets Advanced Analytics Survey \u2013 please participate</h1>\n<div class=\"pagi\">\n<div class=\"pagi-left\">\n<a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/2016/04/data-science-comprehensive-guide-transition.html\" rel=\"prev\"><img height=\"10\" src=\"/images/prv.gif\" width=\"8\"> <strong>Previous post</strong></img></a></div>\n<div class=\"pagi-right\">\n<a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/jobs/16/04-12-rmn-director-data-science-digital-attribution.html\" rel=\"next\"><strong>Next post</strong> <img height=\"10\" src=\"/images/nxt.gif\" width=\"8\"/></a></div>\n<br/>\u00a0<br/>\u00a0\n    <div class=\"addthis_native_toolbox\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"tag-data\">Tags: <a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/tag/advanced-analytics\" rel=\"tag\">Advanced Analytics</a>, <a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/tag/data-scientist\" rel=\"tag\">Data Scientist</a>, <a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/tag/idc\" rel=\"tag\">IDC</a>, <a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/tag/survey\" rel=\"tag\">Survey</a></div>\n<br/>\n<p class=\"excerpt\">\n     What are the use cases for machine learning? What's the typical analytics workflow? Should we have a data science team? Should we outsource our analytics? Help IDC and KDnuggets answer these questions and read the results on KDnuggets and in other places.\n  </p>\n</div>\n<div id=\"post-header-ad\">\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">kda_sid_write(1); kda_sid_n=2;</script>\n</div>\n<hr class=\"grey-line\"/><br/>\n<div class=\"post\" id=\"post-\">\n<p>Today, the data scientists are in high demand globally across industries. With the demand come strategy and execution considerations that many organizations are ill prepared to handle. Questions about technology, process, staffing, and data abound.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://surveyidc2.opinioninsight.com/survey/?ID=683http://\"><img alt=\"idc-survey-word-cloud\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-47128\" height=\"300\" sizes=\"(max-width: 490px) 100vw, 490px\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/idc-survey-word-cloud.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/wp-content/uploads/idc-survey-word-cloud.jpg 490w, https://www.kdnuggets.com/wp-content/uploads/idc-survey-word-cloud-300x183.jpg 300w\" width=\"490\"/></a></p>\n<p>What are the use cases for machine learning? What's the typical analytics workflow? Should we have a data science team? Should we outsource our analytics? What is the extent of interaction between data scientists and their line of business colleagues? Which of the many new and well-established software tools and languages should we evaluate?</p>\n<p>To help answer some of these and  other related questions that are facing today's executives, managers, and staff charged with leading their organization's data science efforts, IDC, the premier technology market research firm and KDnuggets, the leading source for data science related content, have partnered to conduct a survey of the advanced and predictive analytics community.</p>\n<p>This <a href=\"https://surveyidc2.opinioninsight.com/survey/?ID=683\">survey project</a> is being led by <a href=\"http://www.idc.com/getdoc.jsp?containerId=PRF000388\">Dan Vesset</a>, Group VP of Analytics and Information Management market research at IDC and <a href=\"/gps.html\">Gregory Piatetsky-Shapiro</a>, President of KDnuggets. The key results of the survey will be published in an article on KDnuggets as well as in various forms on IDC.com.</p>\n<p>Please take a few minutes to help us assess the state of the data science market today by respond to the survey questions at the <a href=\"https://surveyidc2.opinioninsight.com/survey/?ID=683\">following this link</a>.</p>\n<p>Thank you</p>\n<p>Dan and Gregory</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"page-link\"></div>\n<div class=\"pagi\">\n<hr class=\"grey-line\"/>\n<div class=\"pagi-left\">\n<a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/2016/04/data-science-comprehensive-guide-transition.html\" rel=\"prev\"><img height=\"10\" src=\"/images/prv.gif\" width=\"8\"/> <strong>Previous post</strong></a></div>\n<div class=\"pagi-right\">\n<a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/jobs/16/04-12-rmn-director-data-science-digital-attribution.html\" rel=\"next\"><strong>Next post</strong> <img height=\"10\" src=\"/images/nxt.gif\" width=\"8\"/></a></div>\n<br/><br/>\n<div>\n<hr clas